<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 08:09:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队敦促加沙人南下，但他们担心沿途遭到轰炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-urges-gazans-to-go-south-but-they-fear-being-bombed-along-the-way/0000018b-a017-dc0b-a1cb-e5d772d40000</link><description>玛纳尔的家人选择留在贾巴利亚的避难所；即使通讯畅通，纳迪姆的母亲也不回复短信。他们在加沙北部的家园被摧毁，他们知道以色列打算阻止他们返回以建立安全区</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 07:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-urges-gazans-to-go-south-but-they-fear-being-bombed-along-the-way/0000018b-a017-dc0b-a1cb-e5d772d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地面进攻中丧生；巴勒斯坦人在耶路撒冷刺伤两名边防警察</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-live/jordan-our-air-force-dropped-aid-into-gaza-u-s-deploys-nuclear-submarine-to-middle-east/0000018b-a261-dc41-af9f-eb632d730006</link><description>以色列军队在加沙的地面攻势仍在继续，以色列国防军公布了在战斗中阵亡的士兵姓名 ■ 巴勒斯坦活动家阿赫德·塔米米因涉嫌煽动而被捕 ■ 两名边境警察在耶路撒冷袭击中受伤 ■ 以色列-黎巴嫩边境局势继续紧张 ■ 至少 1,300 人10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀造成平民和士兵死亡，241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部声称有 9,000 多人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 04:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-live/jordan-our-air-force-dropped-aid-into-gaza-u-s-deploys-nuclear-submarine-to-middle-east/0000018b-a261-dc41-af9f-eb632d730006</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长仍然不会看到他和他的政变结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/levin-still-wont-see-that-he-and-his-coup-are-finished/0000018b-a146-dc0b-a1cb-e5c6a3920000</link><description>莱文还没有真正内化他所造成的伤害，以及对他的强烈愤怒，而且显然还不知道，在对他来说最好的情况下，他会默默地离开政治舞台并消失。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 04:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/levin-still-wont-see-that-he-and-his-coup-are-finished/0000018b-a146-dc0b-a1cb-e5c6a3920000</guid></item><item><title>白宫日益担忧：以色列没有退出战略，巴勒斯坦权力机构不急于接管加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/growing-concern-in-wh-israel-has-no-exit-strategy-pa-in-no-rush-to-take-over-gaza/0000018b-a0d4-dc0b-a1cb-e5d6fc0e0000</link><description>消息人士称，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯的印象是，以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡和以色列战时内阁成员迄今为止几乎没有讨论此事</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 04:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/growing-concern-in-wh-israel-has-no-exit-strategy-pa-in-no-rush-to-take-over-gaza/0000018b-a0d4-dc0b-a1cb-e5d6fc0e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的极右翼部长是他的资产，而对以色列来说则是负债</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-his-assets-and-for-israel-a-liability/0000018b-a119-d42c-a9ef-ad7fce690000</link><description>考虑向加沙投掷核弹的部长阿米柴·埃利亚胡只是内塔尼亚胡噩梦联盟自伤的一小部分</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 04:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-his-assets-and-for-israel-a-liability/0000018b-a119-d42c-a9ef-ad7fce690000</guid></item><item><title>解雇以色列极右翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/fire-israels-far-right/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de69890000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 03:19:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/fire-israels-far-right/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de69890000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-a25d-da24-a1cb-b75d0e3b0001</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 02:05:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-a25d-da24-a1cb-b75d0e3b0001</guid></item><item><title>作为巴黎地铁上的犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/being-a-jew-on-the-paris-metro/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de6c390000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 01:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/being-a-jew-on-the-paris-metro/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de6c390000</guid></item><item><title>世界完全声援以色列。然后又恢复原状</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-world-was-in-complete-solidarity-with-israel-then-the-status-quo-returned/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de6ced0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 00:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-world-was-in-complete-solidarity-with-israel-then-the-status-quo-returned/0000018b-a11c-dc0b-a1cb-e5de6ced0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡暗示哈马斯袭击与预备役军人抗议之间存在联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-suggests-link-between-hamas-attack-reservists-protest/0000018b-a133-dc0b-a1cb-e5f725340000</link><description>甘茨呼吁内塔尼亚胡撤回声明，该声明暗示在反对司法政变的抗议期间发出的拒绝预备役的呼吁可能会影响哈马斯领导人的计算</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-suggests-link-between-hamas-attack-reservists-protest/0000018b-a133-dc0b-a1cb-e5f725340000</guid></item><item><title>官员称以色列希望战争结束后对加沙进行安全控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/official-says-israel-will-want-security-control-of-gaza-after-war-ends/0000018b-a110-dc41-af9f-eb32b13b0000</link><description>政治官员计划增加进入加沙的援助，并承认限制援助是向哈马斯施压的无效方法，因为哈马斯领导层并没有被平民的苦难吓倒。一名政治官员表示，即使停火以释放人质，也只是暂时的</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/official-says-israel-will-want-security-control-of-gaza-after-war-ends/0000018b-a110-dc41-af9f-eb32b13b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击一个月后，受害者家属的愤怒激起了反内塔尼亚胡的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-05/ty-article/.highlight/a-month-into-the-war-israels-protest-movement-is-rising-again/0000018b-a07b-da24-a1cb-b77f750f0000</link><description>这一次，以色列的示威活动不是因为担心政府得逞后会发生什么，而是因为那些愿意到天涯海角寻找被绑架亲人的家庭的愤怒</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:23:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-05/ty-article/.highlight/a-month-into-the-war-israels-protest-movement-is-rising-again/0000018b-a07b-da24-a1cb-b77f750f0000</guid></item><item><title>对于德国犹太人来说，对加沙战争的反应带来了噩梦，以及对反犹太主义抬头的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-german-jews-reactions-to-gaza-war-bring-nightmares-fears-over-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-9fed-da24-a1cb-9fed7eb30000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日事件以来，随着反犹太主义袭击激增，德国犹太社区不得不在人身安全方面做出艰难选择，当局试图在集会自由和取缔仇恨言论之间取得平衡</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 18:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-german-jews-reactions-to-gaza-war-bring-nightmares-fears-over-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-9fed-da24-a1cb-9fed7eb30000</guid></item><item><title>“重要的是犹太人加入并表示巴勒斯坦人的生命与其他任何人的生命都具有同等价值”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-important-that-jews-say-that-a-palestinian-life-is-worth-the-same-as-any-other-life/0000018b-a039-dc0b-a1cb-e5ff92280000</link><description>周六，数千名抗议者在法国首都游行，呼吁加沙立即停火。虽然大多数抗议者来自亲巴勒斯坦团体和左派，但也有少数犹太人在那里“抗议和平”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 18:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-important-that-jews-say-that-a-palestinian-life-is-worth-the-same-as-any-other-life/0000018b-a039-dc0b-a1cb-e5ff92280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事训练基地的拉比称“整个国家”都是“我们的”，包括加沙和黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/rabbi-at-israeli-military-base-says-whole-country-is-ours-including-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-a031-d42c-a9ef-ad772cdc0000</link><description>陆军表示，阿米查·弗里德曼的言论与其价值观不符，此前他告诉士兵，以色列将使其在加沙的前定居点看起来“很小”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 17:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/rabbi-at-israeli-military-base-says-whole-country-is-ours-including-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-a031-d42c-a9ef-ad772cdc0000</guid></item><item><title>Amalia Dayan 在纽约从未遇到过反犹太主义 然后到了 10 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amalia-dayan-defends-israel-from-n-y-c-israel-has-terrible-public-relations/0000018b-909c-db7e-af9b-fbdf30b80000</link><description>以色列达扬王朝的艺术品经销商阿玛莉亚·达扬 (Amalia Dayan) 24 岁时移居纽约，并成功开设了一家画廊。艺术界的公开信谴责以色列，却忽略了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀，这让她为人民的叙述而奋斗：“以色列的公共关系很糟糕，”她告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 15:05:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amalia-dayan-defends-israel-from-n-y-c-israel-has-terrible-public-relations/0000018b-909c-db7e-af9b-fbdf30b80000</guid></item><item><title>Twitter 的社区注释如何加速否认哈马斯针对以色列人的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/twitters-community-notes-accelerates-denialism-about-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis/0000018b-9f5b-dbad-abfb-dfdf31200000</link><description>社区笔记功能原本是为了消除 X（以前的 Twitter）上的阴谋论。相反，埃隆·马斯克对众包审核的偏爱是允许恶意用户将有关 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击的仇恨、谎言和虚假信息武器化</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:36:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/twitters-community-notes-accelerates-denialism-about-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis/0000018b-9f5b-dbad-abfb-dfdf31200000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争引发的美国校园反犹太主义给即将上大学的犹太孩子带来了困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-campus-antisemitism-over-gaza-war-creates-dilemma-for-college-bound-jewish-kids/0000018b-9fa8-dbad-abfb-dffce13d0000</link><description>犹太高中生和他们的父母正面临着前所未有的困境：要么安于一所不太知名的大学，在那里他们会觉得作为犹太人更安全，要么瞄准最好的学校，因为他们知道等待他们的可能是充满敌意的校园经历</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-campus-antisemitism-over-gaza-war-creates-dilemma-for-college-bound-jewish-kids/0000018b-9fa8-dbad-abfb-dffce13d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争近距离：与以色列国防军一起进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-what-war-looks-and-sounds-like-a-journey-into-gaza-with-the-idf/0000018b-9f5f-db51-a99b-9fdf49090000</link><description>四周无休无止的破坏，空袭和坦克炮弹的配乐：《国土报》加入加沙地带北部第 36 师的士兵队伍</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-what-war-looks-and-sounds-like-a-journey-into-gaza-with-the-idf/0000018b-9f5f-db51-a99b-9fdf49090000</guid></item><item><title>他用迷人的照片记录了他的军队服役经历。上周他在加沙去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-documented-his-army-service-in-captivating-photos-last-week-his-died-in-gaza/0000018b-9f43-dbad-abfb-dfdfae330000</link><description>以色列参谋军士。 20 岁的拉维·利普希茨 (Lavi Lipshitz) 于上周二在加沙的行动中身亡。这位才华横溢的摄影爱好者在去世前创建了一个 Instagram 页面，展示了用他的富士相机捕捉他服兵役的精彩照片</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 13:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-documented-his-army-service-in-captivating-photos-last-week-his-died-in-gaza/0000018b-9f43-dbad-abfb-dfdfae330000</guid></item></channel></rss>